Title: Kansas City Confidential
Description: An ex-con trying to go straight is framed for a million dollar armored car robbery and must go to Mexico in order to unmask the real culprits.
Short Description: An ex-con is framed for an armored car robbery

Title: Too Late for Tears
Description: Through a fluke circumstance, a ruthless woman stumbles across a suitcase filled with $60,000, and is determined to hold onto it even if it means murder.
Short Description: A woman is determined to hold onto a suitcase filled with $60K even if it means murder

Title: Woman on the Run
Description: Frank Johnson becomes an eyewitness to a murder. He's pursued around San Francisco by his wife, the police, and the killer.
Short Description: A witness to a murder is pursed by his spouse and police.

Title: The Red House
Description: An old man and his sister are concealing a terrible secret from their adopted teen daughter, concerning a hidden abandoned farmhouse, located deep in the woods.
Short Description: An old man is concealing a terrible secret in an old red house deep in the woods

Title: Beat the Devil
Description: On their way to Africa are a group of rogues who hope to get rich there, and a seemingly innocent British couple. They meet and things happen…
Short Description: A group of rogues seek quick riches in Africa.

Title: Flight to Mars
Description: Five astronauts successfully fly to Mars where they encounter seemingly friendly and advanced inhabitants who harbor covert plans to use their ship to invade Earth.
Short Description: Five astronauts fly to Mars and encounter advanced civilizations.

Title: The Stranger
Description: An investigator from the War Crimes Commission travels to Connecticut to find an infamous Nazi.
Short Description: An investigator from the War Crimes Commission travels to Connecticut to find an infamous Nazi.
